1. *Predaleko* si otišao od kuće. (You have gone *too far* from home.)
2. Ne smem da idem *predaleko* odavde. (I cannot go *too far* from here.)
3. Ta ideja je *predaleko* od realnosti. (That idea is *far-fetched* from reality.)
4. *Predaleko* smo otišli sa ovim projektom. (We have gone *too far* with this project.)
5. Ne gledaj *predaleko* u budućnost, fokusiraj se na sadašnjost. (Don't look *too far* into the future, focus on the present.)
6. *Predaleko* odavde nema benzinske pumpe. (There is no gas station *far* from here.)
7. Njen dom je *predaleko* odavde, treba mi sat vremena da stignem tamo. (Her house is *far* from here, it takes me an hour to get there.)
8. Planina je *predaleko* za mene, ne mogu da je osvojim. (The mountain is *too far* for me, I cannot conquer it.)
9. Razmišljanje na taj način je *predaleko* od onoga što želimo postići. (Thinking in that way is *far off* from what we want to achieve.)
10. Dug je put *predaleko* do tamo, bolje se spremite. (The road is *far* to get there, better get ready.)